\par }{\cf0 Charm Monster, Mass
\par }{\fs20\cf0 Enchantment (Charm) [Mind-Affecting]
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Level:}{\fs20\cf0  Brd 6, Sor/Wiz 8
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Components:}{\fs20\cf0  V
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Targets:}{\fs20\cf0  One or more creatures, no two of which can be more than 30 ft. apart
\par }{\b\fs20\cf0 Duration:}{\fs20\cf0  One day/level
\par This spell functions like }{\i\fs20\cf0 charm monster, }{\fs20\cf0 except that }{\i\fs20\cf0 mass charm monster }{\fs20\cf0 
affects a number of creatures whose combined HD do not exceed twice your level, or at least one creature regardless of HD. If there are more potential targets than you can affect, you choose them one at a time until you choose a creature with too many HD.

